---
layout: layouts/prime_layout.njk
coverImg: assets/logo.jpg
coverTitle: The NeedleMaid
custom_cover_img: full-round index-logo
eleventyNavigation:
  key: Home
  order: 0
---
<div class="page home-page">
  <section class="info info-text">
    <h1>Our story</h1>
    <p>
      Imagine a land of peace and music and aroma of delicacies. A land where clouds cast a magic mist and trains scale the peaks with an old age charm. Darjeeling - inarguably, the "Queen of Hills".
    </p>
    <p>
      Sourced from the foothills of the Himalayas, we present an exclusive collection of fabric merchandise.
      Carefully selected fabrics that shine the light of smiles and manifest the radiant artistic fervour.
      And then meticulously crafted by hand into substance of desires that leave you elated and wanting for more.
    </p>
    <p>
      Luxurious. Hand-made. Sustainable. Zero waste. Rebel.
    </p>
    <p>
      Imagine fabric. Imagine us.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="info">
    <h1>Collections</h1>
    <div class="card-grid">
      {% for item in homepage.collections %}
        <div class="card">
          <a href="/collections/{{item.name}}">
            <img
              src="{{item.img_url}}"
              loading="lazy"
              class="card-media"
              alt="{{item.alt}}"/>
          </a>
          <div class="card-details center">
            <h3 class="card-head">{{item.name}}</h3>
          </div>
        </div>
      {% endfor %}

        <div class="card more-card">
          <div class="card-details">
            <h3 class="card-head">
              <a href="/collections/">And more...</a>
            </h3>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</div>
